    {
      "id": "69cb6bf5d79351be3b28a99e",
      "text": "謎解き2026/03/31",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939139,
      "updated": 1774939139
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6db50000000000ed5685",
      "text": "[~ 白い矢印を使って]炎上してる謎解きがあり、関連して[~ 白い図形を使ったもの]がガンガンでてきてて面白い[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939573,
      "updated": 1774939908
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6db50000000000ed5686",
      "text": ">[dUgBZdz8Ti28134 https://x.com/dUgBZdz8Ti28134/status/2038279608391585867] #あかさなぞ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939573,
      "updated": 1774939724
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6e4c0000000000ed5687",
      "text": "> [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HElsR7hasAABgyz?format=png&name=medium#.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939724,
      "updated": 1774939724
    },
    {
      "id": "69cba93c0000000000ed56f7",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774954812,
      "updated": 1774954815
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6e4c0000000000ed5688",
      "text": "\t[~ 白い矢印があって全然見えない]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939724,
      "updated": 1774954812
    },
    {
      "id": "69cba9330000000000ed56f4",
      "text": "\t[~ 白い矢印があって全然見えない]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774954804,
      "updated": 1774954811
    },
    {
      "id": "69cba9420000000000ed56f8",
      "text": "\t[~ うし→ね　ね→い　から十二支だと判断して、]こたえは[~ 「こたつ」]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774954818,
      "updated": 1774954883
    },
    {
      "id": "69cba93b0000000000ed56f6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774954811,
      "updated": 1774954811
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6e790000000000ed56a0",
      "text": ">[Spicy_boh103 https://x.com/Spicy_boh103/status/2038497271550242928] なんか白矢印のギミックに賛否が分かれてるらしいけど「白い矢印がある」っていうひらめきまでたどり着くのが難しい人もいることに気づいてハッとしたなあ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939770,
      "updated": 1774939770
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6e790000000000ed56a1",
      "text": "> 自分の謎はこのギミック多用してるから気になってないのかもしらん…",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939770,
      "updated": 1774939770
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6e930000000000ed56c4",
      "text": "> [https://gyazo.com/112c9d0748183e0dd971c21447ac27d8]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939796,
      "updated": 1774939797
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6e800000000000ed56c2",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939776,
      "updated": 1774954873
    },
    {
      "id": "69cba9780000000000ed56f9",
      "text": "\t[~ 英語で3文字で濡れるのがWETだとすると、英語はWxyTE、日本語は?xy?O]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774954873,
      "updated": 1774954964
    },
    {
      "id": "69cba9d90000000000ed56fa",
      "text": "\t[~ 白い矢印がギミックに使われていることからWHITEだろうと推測すると、日本語は?HI?OなのでSHIROだろう]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774954970,
      "updated": 1774955015
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbaa080000000000ed56fb",
      "text": "\t[~ 答えるべき答えは白い矢印に従ってSHIRT、白いシャツということか]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774955016,
      "updated": 1774955050
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbaa2a0000000000ed56fc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774955051,
      "updated": 1774955051
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6c770000000000ed564b",
      "text": ">[saikoro2357 https://x.com/saikoro2357/status/2038697337363849361] 逆に言っちゃうって方向性で面白いのが出来ないのかなって思ったんで、一旦タグだけ生やします。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939255,
      "updated": 1774939555
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6da20000000000ed5653",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939555,
      "updated": 1774939555
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6da20000000000ed5654",
      "text": "> もし何か思いついたらあげてみてほしいです。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939555,
      "updated": 1774939555
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6da20000000000ed5655",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939555,
      "updated": 1774939555
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6da20000000000ed5656",
      "text": "> #この謎には白い図形が含まれます",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939555,
      "updated": 1774939555
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6da20000000000ed5657",
      "text": "> [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HErnjaQbcAAKpwS?format=jpg&name=medium#.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939555,
      "updated": 1774939555
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6da20000000000ed5658",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939555,
      "updated": 1774955058
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbaa310000000000ed56ff",
      "text": "\t[~ ば、ばぐ、ばぐん]、[~ 「ん」を1つ増やすのに矢印4つも使うので、4回何かをするという意味ではないと判断]、[~ 1がグで2がンと考えると「グリーン」だなとなる]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774955058,
      "updated": 1774955143
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbaa300000000000ed56fd",
      "text": "\t\t[~ も、もん、もんく　が　ピンク　と同じルールで再現されるので解釈正しそう]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774955056,
      "updated": 1774955176
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbaaac0000000000ed5700",
      "text": "\t\t[~ その下の何も見えないところに白い矢印があって「ホワイト」だと考えると、か、かい、かいわ、になる]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774955180,
      "updated": 1774955214
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbaa300000000000ed56fe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774955056,
      "updated": 1774955056
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6db00000000000ed5684",
      "text": "というのをまとめようとしたら僕のTwitterまとめ用のChrome拡張が関連ツイートも拾うのでたくさん謎が収穫されてしまったw[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939569,
      "updated": 1774939905
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6c6c0000000000ed564a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939244,
      "updated": 1774939244
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6eb00000000000ed56ca",
      "text": ">[turbot_kare https://x.com/turbot_kare/status/2038564301158637984] これを見て[~ 弓矢]だなぁと思う皆様におかれましては",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939825,
      "updated": 1774939951
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6eb00000000000ed56cb",
      "text": "> [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HEpvbW2bcAAf7X4?format=jpg&name=medium#.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939825,
      "updated": 1774939825
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6eb00000000000ed56cc",
      "text": "\t[~ マス目と黒い四角を見ただけで五十音表のや行を連想する人向け][nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939825,
      "updated": 1774940266
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6eb00000000000ed56cd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939825,
      "updated": 1774939825
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6eb00000000000ed56ce",
      "text": ">[Ozone_Nazo0803 https://x.com/Ozone_Nazo0803/status/2038750942229823798] 謎解きはこれくらいフリーダムに作ってますよ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939825,
      "updated": 1774939825
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6eb00000000000ed56cf",
      "text": "> [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HEsZLQEakAADMMa?format=jpg&name=medium#.png] [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HEsZLQDaIAEM4HL?format=jpg&name=medium#.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939825,
      "updated": 1774939825
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6eb00000000000ed56d0",
      "text": "\t情報多すぎてよくわからない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939825,
      "updated": 1774940008
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6f670000000000ed56ef",
      "text": "\t\t[~ 除夜の鐘で鍛冶屋なのはさておき、色や影やアイコンに意味があるのか、アイコンを見て誰かわかることを前提にしているならnot for meだよなとか]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774940008,
      "updated": 1774940061
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6f9d0000000000ed56f0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774940062,
      "updated": 1774940063
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6eb00000000000ed56d1",
      "text": ">[nazonodesigner https://x.com/nazonodesigner/status/2038813549007417528] このパズルが解けますか？ #nazzle",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939825,
      "updated": 1774939825
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6eb00000000000ed56d2",
      "text": "> [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HEolkq8b0AAPb7G?format=jpg&name=medium#.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939825,
      "updated": 1774939825
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6eb00000000000ed56d3",
      "text": "\t情報少なすぎて何からしたらいいかわからない[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939825,
      "updated": 1774940086
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6fb30000000000ed56f1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774940084,
      "updated": 1774940084
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6fb30000000000ed56f2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774940084,
      "updated": 1774940084
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6eb00000000000ed56d4",
      "text": ">[silsil91046 https://x.com/silsil91046/status/2038820311559545334] 誰かこれをポストすると思ってたのに観測されなかったので負け",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939825,
      "updated": 1774939825
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6eb00000000000ed56d5",
      "text": "> [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HEtYQ7-bIAAJ1cU?format=jpg&name=medium#.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939825,
      "updated": 1774939825
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6eb00000000000ed56d6",
      "text": "\t答えはわかるんだけど赤いゾーンがわからない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939825,
      "updated": 1774939825
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6eb00000000000ed56d7",
      "text": "\t\tと書き込みに来たら[~ これ赤じゃなくてピンクか]わかった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939825,
      "updated": 1774939825
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6eb00000000000ed56d8",
      "text": "\t\t [Cosenseからは頭の良くなる電波が出てる]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939825,
      "updated": 1774939825
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6eb00000000000ed56d9",
      "text": "\t\t[~ みどり、みずいろ、むらさきいろ、きいろ、ぴんく、くろ、1のところは見えない白い矢印がある]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939825,
      "updated": 1774955525
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbabfa0000000000ed5701",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774955514,
      "updated": 1774955515
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6eb00000000000ed56da",
      "text": ">[kino1048576 https://x.com/kino1048576/status/2038769060239044688] まあまあ、みんなこういうスラム街みたいな謎解きを見て落ち着いてもろて",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939825,
      "updated": 1774939825
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6eb00000000000ed56db",
      "text": "> [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HEspp26bUAAERnO?format=jpg&name=medium#.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939825,
      "updated": 1774939825
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6eb00000000000ed56dc",
      "text": "\t全然わからない[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939825,
      "updated": 1774955564
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbac1b0000000000ed5703",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774955548,
      "updated": 1774955548
    },
