    {
      "id": "69cb6eb10000000000ed56ee",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939826,
      "updated": 1774939826
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6ea00000000000ed56c6",
      "text": ">[Spicy_boh103 https://x.com/Spicy_boh103/status/2038497278709899747] ここらへんとかは特にひどいね",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939809,
      "updated": 1774939809
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6ea10000000000ed56c7",
      "text": "> 悪意しかないデザインにわざわざしてますから↓",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939809,
      "updated": 1774939809
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6ea10000000000ed56c8",
      "text": "> [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HEoyeMobEAAGKGn?format=jpg&name=small#.png] [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HEoyeMobkAAnly0?format=jpg&name=small#.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939809,
      "updated": 1774939809
    },
    {
      "id": "69cb6ea10000000000ed56c9",
      "text": "\t何を求められているのか皆目見当がつかない[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774939809,
      "updated": 1774955755
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbacd90000000000ed5707",
      "text": "\t\t[~ 左の四角に尻尾が生えてるのは何？]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774955738,
      "updated": 1774955756
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbacd90000000000ed5706",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774955738,
      "updated": 1774955738
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbb85e0000000000ed5708",
      "text": ">[gaasuuquestion https://x.com/gaasuuquestion/status/2037863524031238505] 答えが3つある問題です。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774958687,
      "updated": 1774958687
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbb85f0000000000ed5709",
      "text": "> [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HEaqfeZagAE0dQO?format=jpg&name=medium#.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774958687,
      "updated": 1774958687
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbb85f0000000000ed570a",
      "text": "\t一つ目は[~ いか]？[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774958687,
      "updated": 1774958760
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbb86d0000000000ed5716",
      "text": "\t\t3つあるとはどういうことか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774958701,
      "updated": 1774958758
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbb8a60000000000ed5717",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774958758,
      "updated": 1774958758
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbb8a60000000000ed5718",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774958758,
      "updated": 1774958758
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbb85f0000000000ed570e",
      "text": ">[Hattenazo https://x.com/Hattenazo/status/2038929445667696727] そもそも謎解きは「その数字で4桁錠が開く」とか「URLを書き換えると次のSTEPへ行ける」とかの問題外の要素で確定を取っていたので、問題画像だけで確定を取っている一枚謎文化の方が異質",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774958687,
      "updated": 1774958687
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbb85f0000000000ed570f",
      "text": "なるほどな〜[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774958687,
      "updated": 1774959372
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbbb0a0000000000ed5719",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774959371,
      "updated": 1774959371
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbb8660000000000ed5715",
      "text": ">[maruten1420 https://x.com/maruten1420/status/2038923314677358771] 謎解きにおける「理不尽」ってこういう謎だと思うんですけど",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774958695,
      "updated": 1774960099
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbbde20000000000ed571d",
      "text": "> [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HEu18l5bUAAccx5?format=jpg&name=medium#.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774960099,
      "updated": 1774960099
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbbde20000000000ed571f",
      "text": ">[maruten1420 https://x.com/maruten1420/status/2038927229296751099] 【解説】",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774960099,
      "updated": 1774960099
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbbde20000000000ed5720",
      "text": "> [~ フリック入力]の表っぽいですね",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774960099,
      "updated": 1774960119
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbbde20000000000ed5721",
      "text": "> 1～5を読んで答えは「[~ あからさま]」に…？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774960099,
      "updated": 1774960123
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbbde20000000000ed5723",
      "text": ">[maruten1420 https://x.com/maruten1420/status/2038927779572707586] 上の部分に「あからさま」な空白がありますね",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774960099,
      "updated": 1774960099
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbbde20000000000ed5724",
      "text": "> 目を凝らして読むと次のような指示が現れます",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774960099,
      "updated": 1774960099
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbbde20000000000ed5725",
      "text": "> (目を凝らさなくてもペイント機能を使ってバケツ塗りするとちゃんと出てきます)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774960099,
      "updated": 1774960099
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbbde20000000000ed5726",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774960099,
      "updated": 1774960099
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbbde20000000000ed5727",
      "text": "> ということで1～5を読んで正解は「CHEAT」に…？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774960099,
      "updated": 1774960099
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbbde20000000000ed5728",
      "text": "> [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HEu5lWMakAAv7yM?format=png&name=medium#.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774960099,
      "updated": 1774960099
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbbde20000000000ed5729",
      "text": "\tは？w[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774960099,
      "updated": 1774960175
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbbde20000000000ed572a",
      "text": ">[maruten1420 https://x.com/maruten1420/status/2038928138160513034] いやいや、最初の黒部分も立派な「背景」ですよね",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774960099,
      "updated": 1774960099
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbbde20000000000ed572b",
      "text": "> ちゃんとここも目を凝らして読んでください",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774960099,
      "updated": 1774960099
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbbde20000000000ed572c",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774960099,
      "updated": 1774960099
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbbde20000000000ed572d",
      "text": "> 数字は黒色の方を使うようです",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774960099,
      "updated": 1774960099
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbbde20000000000ed572e",
      "text": "> ということで1～5を読んで正解は「TRICK」でした！",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774960099,
      "updated": 1774960099
    },
    {
      "id": "69cbbde20000000000ed572f",
